{"tid":45300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：傅家俊體現港人永不放棄逆境自強","createTime":"2016-12-19T01:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T01:52:54.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e33405bd37124bb2c43c67a57b61b2efafefee1b","tid":45300,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mLzK4F8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLzK4F8.jpg&h=e80284c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港桌球手傅家俊在蘇格蘭公開賽，先落後下連追多局奪標。行政長官梁振英早上在facebook發文恭賀，讚揚傅家俊體現港人永不放棄、逆境自強精神。<br />\n<br />\n傅家俊的決賽對手是世界排名第三的希堅斯，傅在比賽中一度落後局數0比3，在第一節賽事完結前追至4比4平手，其後再連贏多局，最終在17局9勝制的比賽中，以9比4勝出，是他歷來第3個排名賽錦標。<br />\n<br />\n特首梁振英今早在facebook恭賀傅家俊，指傅家俊在一度落後的劣勢下沉着應戰，終連追8局「逆轉勝」，讚揚他「完美體現港人永不放棄，逆境自強的精神」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161219/s00001/1482108744180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161219%2Fs00001%2F1482108744180&d=en1O0unu1ryP%2FPqfndsG5EsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=8bbddaf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161219%2Fs00001%2F1482108744180&h=ee1e9ce1\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161219/s00001/1482108744180</a>"},{"pid":"127e584a5f9bfc0cb99d4fbbdb41e4559a640149","tid":45300,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i61.tinypic.com/152kso2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi61.tinypic.com%2F152kso2.jpg&h=fde3445b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd17984e798d4b1f5ce254b01488024e59b0c880","tid":45300,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:23:02.000Z","msg":"行撚開啦屌你老味"},{"pid":"854cc0d6c0b7e59978bfcc20ee5d11c29cf7658d","tid":45300,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci